    good value and a better experience than anywhere else.  We're faster; You can arrange an entire funeral in less than anywhere else.  We're safer; there is no need to visit multiple funeral homes, you can do
    everything you need in the app.  We're focused on user satisfaction: we manage all the task that comes from your purchase. You don't need to run after the funeral director for confirmations, the caterer for scones or the florist to confirm details and deliveries.
     We manage everything on your behalf and keep you informed all the way. We are completely changing the way people approach death care by digitizing funeral &amp; related services."
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:textSize="20sp"
                            tools:ignore="HardcodedText" />


                    </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>


                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>

