You can then continue selecting services and products that you want. When you're ready, you can click on the checkout icon at the bottom of the screen and you will be taken to the checkout screen."
                        android:textColor="@color/black"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        tools:ignore="HardcodedText" />
                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>


